<li><a href="/wiki/Henry_Adams" title="Henry Adams">Henry Adams</a>'s novel <i><a href="/wiki/Democracy:_An_American_Novel" title="Democracy: An American Novel">Democracy</a></i> (<a href="/wiki/1880_in_literature" title="1880 in literature">1880</a>)</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Carl_Hiaasen" title="Carl Hiaasen">Carl Hiaasen</a>'s novel <i><a href="/wiki/Sick_Puppy" title="Sick Puppy">Sick Puppy</a></i> (<a href="/wiki/1999_in_literature" title="1999 in literature">1999</a>)</li>
<li>Much of the <a href="/wiki/Batman" title="Batman">Batman</a> comic book series</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/V_for_Vendetta" title="V for Vendetta">V for Vendetta</a></i> comic book series</li>
